  "text": "The hypocotyls of 3-d-old etiolated seedlings were used for live-cell imaging. Imaging was performed on a Yokogawa CSUX1spinning disk system as described previously [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Image analysis was performed using Metamorph (Molecular Devices), ImageJ software (version 1.43u; http://rsbweb.nih.gov/ij/), and Imaris (Bitplane) software. CESA particle density measurements and CESA particle dynamics analysis were performed as described previously [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] .",
